properties.Name: HydrocrackerUnitComponentType
properties.Description:
A type  of hydrocracker unit component that may be integrated with or supporting the operation of the hydrocracker unit.

Ex:
- Reactor
- Debutanizer column
- Fractionator column
- Gas oil stripper
- Kerosene stripper
- Heavy naphtha splitter
- Heat Exchanger
- Water-cooled Condenser
- Sour water Stripper
- Amine gas treating unit
- Feed charge pump
- Recycle furnace
- High pressure separators
